aza Oatmeal Milk \u0026amp; Honey Soap\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: left;\"\u003eTaza Oatmeal Milk \u0026amp; Honey Soap is known for its soothing effect on your skin and it has the ability to reduce irritation and dryness. The texture of this soap also acts as a natural exfoliant, leaving your skin feeling soft and smooth. The honey in this soap helps keep moisture locked in your skin. This moisture and elasticity help to give your skin its natural glow and healthy look. \u003c\/p\u003e","products":[{"product_id":"taza-natural-botanical-extract-facial-cleanser","title":"Taza Natural Botanical Extract Facial Cleanser","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: small;\" size=\"6\"\u003e*Free Standard Shipping\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/em\u003e; \u003cem\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: small;\" size=\"6\"\u003e*Orders from this site Fulfillment by Amazon.ca;\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/em\u003e \u003cem\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: small;\" size=\"6\"\u003e*Secure \u0026amp; Protected Cardholder Data Processing with Shopify Payments\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/em\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eTaza Natural Botanical Extract Facial Cleanser\u003c\/b\u003e is a mild botanical-based cleanser that is formulated to thoroughly cleanse the skin without stripping away essential moisture. This product contains: Chamomile Extract, Aloe Leaf Juice, Cucumber Extract, and Japanese Green Tea Extract. The following are benefits of these ingredients:\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eThe Chamomile Extract eases the itching of eczema and other rashes and reduces skin inflammation, is also speeds healing and prevents bacterial infection.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eThe Cucumber Extract contains various minerals including magnesium, potassium, and silica. Silica can help reduce the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles. It also helps minimize the appearance of pores.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u0